sources.title: Shell Shock (1964) BEACH DICKERSON
sources.description:
Exclusive FRIDAY at PizzaFLIX Edition!
Directed by: John Patrick Hayes
Starring: Beach Dickerson, Frank Leo, Pamela Grey

A decorated G.I. goes AWOL after suffering from Shell Shock. His sadistic sergeant claims he was faking, but must rescue him from behind enemy lines to prove it!

sources.title: Shell Shock (1964) Drama, War
sources.description:
On the front in Italy during WW 2, a sergeant thinks that one of his men is faking battle fatigue, and sets out to expose him.

Director: John Hayes 
Writers: Randy Fields, John Hayes
Stars: Beach Dickerson, Carl Crow, Frank Leo
Genres: Drama, War
